# <type>: <description>
#
# Types: feat, fix, chore, hotfix, refactor, docs, test, ci, perf
#
# Good examples:
#   feat: add channel messages dashboard view
#   fix: show sender name on synced messages
#   refactor: replace em dash with hyphen in copy
#   chore: centralize app branding in env vars
#
# Rules (strict — husky commit-msg hook):
#   - First line only, 10-100 characters
#   - Format: <type>: <description>
#   - Description starts with lowercase
#   - No periods, no em dash, no multi-sentence summaries
#
# Bad (will be rejected):
#   Refactor various components to improve formatting consistency...
#   Update deployment branch to dev, enhance navigation by adding...
#   feat: Add Something With Title Case
